.TH DEUTERIUMCOIN-CLI "1" "February 2016" "deuteriumcoin-cli 0.12"
.SH NAME
deuteriumcoin-cli \- a remote procedure call client for Deuteriumcoin Core. 
.SH SYNOPSIS
deuteriumcoin-cli [options] <command> [params] \- Send command to Deuteriumcoin Core. 
.TP
deuteriumcoin-cli [options] help \- Asks Deuteriumcoin Core for a list of supported commands.
.SH DESCRIPTION
This manual page documents the deuteriumcoin-cli program. deuteriumcoin-cli is an RPC client used to send commands to Deuteriumcoin Core.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-?\fR
Show possible options.

.SH "SEE ALSO"
\fBdeuteriumcoind\fP, \fBdeuteriumcoin.conf\fP
